INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following in the distribution
directory:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or simply copy EasyTool.pm to your lib path

To uninstall this module type the following:

rm -rdf `cat /usr/lib/perl5/site_perl/5.8.5/i386-linux-thread-multi/auto/EasyTool/.packlist` /usr/lib/perl5/site_perl/5.8.5/i386-linux-thread-multi/auto/EasyTool


